      <title>波音公司與 Spirit 同意簽署 4.25 億美元協議以解決供應商問題</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/spirit-boeing-enter-into-memorandum-agreement-improve-aero-suppliers-issues-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spirit AeroSystems表示，在美國航空監管機構限制該飛機製造商的737 MAX產量後，波音公司將向其支付4.25億美元的預付款，並幫助其解決庫存水平較高和現金流減少等問題。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/spirit-boeing-enter-into-memorandum-agreement-improve-aero-suppliers-issues-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:37:03 GMT</pubDate>
